788
00:44:43,900 --> 00:44:45,230
the biggest in the United States,

789
00:44:45,500 --> 00:44:47,900
and it is being pumped dry.

790
00:44:48,800 --> 00:44:51,720
Already, California faces
massive water shortages,

791
00:44:51,720 --> 00:44:54,375
because the snowpack
in the Sierra Nevada Mountains

792
00:44:54,375 --> 00:44:59,250
