and the aquifers there too are running dry.

793
00:45:00,000 --> 00:45:02,610
No water, no food.

794
00:45:03,075 --> 00:45:06,465
Every one of the 6 major bread baskets
faces new risks.

795
00:45:06,465 --> 00:45:10,384
And by 2050, researchers believe
that 1 year out of 3,

796
00:45:10,384 --> 00:45:14,295
two breadbaskets or more
will fail at the same time,

797
00:45:14,655 --> 00:45:17,124
leading to hunger and social unrest.


798
00:45:18,069 --> 00:45:20,664
The risks on the food system
are piling on,

799
00:45:20,664 --> 00:45:24,398
just when we need to find a way
to feed 2 more billion people.

800
00:45:26,505 --> 00:45:30,700
It’s hard also to imagine
how we’ll avoid terrible wars.

