00:45:34,290 --> 00:45:36,390
India and Pakistan will be parched.


803
00:45:36,750 --> 00:45:41,341
In red again here the zones so hot
it will be almost unlivable.

804
00:45:42,780 --> 00:45:46,280
India and Pakistan, that's 2 billion people
with nowhere to go.





805
00:45:46,910 --> 00:45:49,689
Trapped between the Himalayas
and the Indian Ocean.

806
00:45:50,409 --> 00:45:51,485
You know, in two countries

807
00:45:51,485 --> 00:45:53,665
who are already have
tense military relationships.

808
00:45:53,665 --> 00:45:56,039
They both have nuclear weapons.

809
00:45:56,334 --> 00:45:58,621
And so do seven other countries
in the world.

810
00:46:02,930 --> 00:46:03,820
Closer to home,

811
00:46:03,820 --> 00:46:08,740
it sometimes feels like our democracies
