813
00:46:14,571 --> 00:46:17,995
When there’ll be millions of
internal and external refugees

814
00:46:18,490 --> 00:46:21,205
and tensions rise to a whole new level?


815
00:46:23,634 --> 00:46:27,595
When some towns get saved
with expensive infrastructure

816
00:46:27,595 --> 00:46:29,169
and others not.

817
00:46:30,159 --> 00:46:32,694
And when there’ll be food shortages.


818
00:46:32,874 --> 00:46:35,895
Will there be riots and violence?


819
00:46:36,660 --> 00:46:38,865
These are all legitimate questions!

820
00:46:39,720 --> 00:46:42,409
And perhaps you think
that we shouldn’t worry.

821
00:46:42,409 --> 00:46:45,189
But the fact
that we are even discussing this,

822
00:46:45,189 --> 00:46:49,470
discussing if these dominoes will fall
