823
00:46:49,470 --> 00:46:52,543
That in itself feels crazy to me!

824
00:46:53,615 --> 00:46:56,425
And we know this is
a lot of information to take in.

825
00:46:56,425 --> 00:47:00,345
You know, if you,
if you need to stretch for a second,

826
00:47:00,660 --> 00:47:02,650
or move around,


